titles: Nice, cozy, warm big bed apartment
descriptions: I am happy to welcome you to my apartment in the city center! Three words: location, cosy and chic!
Peaceful studio in the most wanted area in town. Quiet house Near of everything. Completely renovated. Lovely neighbourhood, lot of trendy shops, restaurants and bars in a walking distance.

This is a place for dreamers to reset, reflect, and create. Designed with a 'slow' pace in mind, our hope is that you enjoy every part of your stay; from making local coffee by drip in the morning, choosing the perfect record to put on as the sun sets.
Discover daily local life in city center, friendly neighborhood, clandestine casino, karaoke, old-style artisans, art gallery and artist studio downstairs.
Design interior in most sympathetic area! Completely renovated, well-equipped, cosy studio in idyllic, over 100 years old wooden house. Calm street, fast connection to center and airport.
reviewTexts: A quiet cozy and picturesque that hides behind a a river by the unique lightness of Amsterdam.
Bathed in the nature. Completely unplugged. Unforgettable.
We loved it so much, the house, the veiw, the location just great.. Highly reccomend :)
The room was spacious and clean. The pool looked nothing like the photos and desparately needs a clean. The sauna and spa were closed for lunar new year holiday.
Home is amazing. It's like staying in a museum. The rooms, furnishings and artworks are incredible. The views of My Vesuvius
I stayed here for one night and it was an unpleasant experience.
This villa is perfect in every way: the view on mountains and waterfalls, the hot tub and the villa itself. The evening here became a great continuation of our journeys over country.
